name: The Allman Brothers Band
profile:
American rock / blues band once based in Macon, Georgia. Formed after the split of [a1549618] and after the [m=253443] album recorded 1968-05 with [a293480].
Years active: 1969-1976, 1978-1982, 1989-2014.
Inducted into Rock And Roll Hall of Fame in 1995 (Performer).
namevariations: ザ・オールマン・ブラザーズ・バンド
